data.description: You'll want to check this one our right away.  Great floorpan & located on 1 of biggest / best lots in the neighborhood. Also adjacent to 1.07 acres of green space giving more privacy extra yard space close by.  Conveniently located in the first cul de sac  as you come into one of the most highly desirable communities in this area.  The Gables At Kepley Farms is a vibrant & active community full of great people living their best lives.  Great location, easy access to lots of cultural & recreational activities: symphony, 3 theater groups, antique & collectable shopping, a planetarium, a renowned genealogical library, many parks, 8 golf courses & lakes, streams, & ponds for fishing.  Community center piece is  4000 square feet clubhouse that has scheduled activities, community can also use fitness center, library, movies, & games, & TV.  Wood floors, Fireplace, Sun / Screen Porch.  55+ community, HOA is $130/mo includes lawn care, no fences.
